headline: CME Group to offer cardano, chainlink, stellar futures as institutions seek regulated risk-management tools
summary: The new futures contracts, available in micro and standard sizes, are set to launch on Feb. 9, pending regulatory approval.

headline: CME Group to Launch Cardano, Chainlink, and Stellar Crypto Futures on February 9
summary: CME Group plans to launch Cardano, Chainlink, and Stellar futures in February, expanding institutional access to major altcoins.
